{
  "stem": "3804.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I say, whatever will happen will happen to all of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my mother felt that this is the last moment, did not go out, you will never get the certificate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She was also afraid from the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They wouldn't give the certificate because it was a big line to get the certificate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you should know always, it's like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That the first who have the good connection, get the certificate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So it was very difficult to get it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And remember at the time of [INAUDIBLE], we go back farther later to Hungary, that only the people get who get the certificate are the relatives [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And some people that been going on, the other people wanted them to go out, and very little who-- who-- who because of other reasons went out.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it's always-- you know, it has some kind of priorities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother was very afraid of priorities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she knew-- she was very, very clever that even as a child and later, I didn't really-- didn't understand it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after it, I understood well when I read-- when I read this book of Ben Hecht.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Pregidy.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Pregidy you say?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Perjury.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Perjury.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and that shows you that it was a big fight, how do you say, to get-- to get-- who will be the first.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother understood, if not now, nobody will be safe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think she was right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There are some family, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- [LAUGHS] Normally, when they ask me, my-- my father-- it's a kind of a joke.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was true.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometime after the war, long ago, somebody come to him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He wanted to show how he is relative to him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, look, if I hate somebody, he's my relative.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
